items.fromString:
We are creating an endpoint which will return data from the legacy based on the individual_system_id give on the endpoint.

Data Structure:


{code:sql}CREATE TABLE dbo.LegacyDataCDH (
	Id UNIQUEIDENTIFIER not null, --gerado em código
	individual_system_id UNIQUEIDENTIFIER not null,
	individual_id int,
	employer_id int,
	employer_alias varchar(6),
	admin_id int,
	admin_alias char(3),
	nav varchar(50)
){code}



Endpoint:

{noformat}GET /persons/v2/legacy-data/cdh?individual_system_id=432C433E-F36B-1410-884A-001BA86B4410{noformat}
